{"formatVersion":"1","manifest":{"sourceId":"kabir-hi","displayName":"कबीर दोहे","displayNameEnglish":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","version":"1.0","language":"Hindi","languageCode":"hi","script":"Devanagari","isRTL":false,"transliterationAvailable":false,"edition":"Public Domain & Curated / Hindi Wikiquote","primaryCategory":"Philosophy & Spirituality","subcategory":"Hindi Wisdom","type":"quotes","browseOrder":"sequence","supportsRandom":true,"supportsBrowse":true,"groupingLevels":[],"groupingLabels":[],"sortPriority":50,"contentRating":"devotional","audienceTags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"itemCount":92,"dataPath":"Data/Collections/KabirDohas_Hindi.json"},"data":[{"id":"kabir-hi-0001","text":"काल करे सो आज कर, आज करे सो अब।\nपल में परलय होएगी, बहुरि करेगा कब॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0002","text":"दुख में सुमिरन सब करे, सुख में करे न कोय।\nजो सुख में सुमिरन करे, तो दुख काहे को होय॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0003","text":"बड़ा हुआ तो क्या हुआ, जैसे पेड़ खजूर।\nपंथी को छाया नहीं, फल लागे अति दूर॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0004","text":"माटी कहे कुम्हार से, तू क्या रोंदे मोय।\nएक दिन ऐसा आएगा, मैं रोंदूंगी तोय॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0005","text":"जब मैं था तब हरि नहीं, अब हरि हैं मैं नाहिं।\nप्रेम गली अति सांकरी, ता में दो न समाहिं॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0006","text":"पोथी पढ़ि पढ़ि जग मुआ, पंडित भया न कोय।\nढाई आखर प्रेम का, पढ़े सो पंडित होय॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0007","text":"साईं इतना दीजिए, जा में कुटुम समाय।\nमैं भी भूखा न रहूं, साधु न भूखा जाय॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0008","text":"लूट सके तो लूट ले, राम नाम की लूट।\nपाछे फिर पछताएगा, जब प्राण जाएंगे छूट॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0009","text":"अति का भला न बोलना, अति की भली न चूप।\nअति का भला न बरसना, अति की भली न धूप॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0010","text":"चाह मिटी, चिंता मिटी, मनवा बेपरवाह।\nजिनको कुछ नहीं चाहिए, वे शाहन के शाह॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0011","text":"गुरु गोबिंद दोउ खड़े, काके लागूं पाँय।\nबलिहारी गुरु आपनो, गोबिंद दियो बताय॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0012","text":"बुरा जो देखन मैं चला, बुरा न मिलिया कोय।\nजो मन खोजा अपना, मुझसे बुरा न कोय॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0013","text":"जैसी प्रीति कुटुंब की, तैसी होय न और।\nप्रीति तो हरि सूं करो, यह अनत नाहीं ठौर॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0014","text":"हिन्दू कहें मोहि राम पियारा, तुर्क कहें रहमाना।\nआपस में दोउ लड़ी-लड़ी मुए, मरम न कोउ जाना॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0015","text":"माला फेरत जुग भया, फिरा न मन का फेर।\nकर का मनका डार दे, मन का मनका फेर॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0016","text":"कबीरा सोया क्या करे, उठि न भजे भगवान।\nजम जब घर ले जाएगा, पड़ा रहेगा म्यान॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0017","text":"मन के हारे हार है, मन के जीते जीत।\nपारब्रह्म को पाइए, मन ही की परतीत॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0018","text":"धीरे-धीरे रे मना, धीरे सब कुछ होय।\nमाली सींचे सौ घड़ा, ऋतु आए फल होय॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0019","text":"राम बुलावा भेजिया, दिया कबीरा रोय।\nजो सुख साधु संग में, सो बैकुंठ न होय॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0020","text":"करता था तो क्यों रहया, जब करि क्यों पछिताय।\nबोया पेड़ बबूल का, आम कहाँ से खाय॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0021","text":"आए हैं सो जाएंगे, राजा रंक फकीर।\nएक सिंहासन चढि चले, एक बंधे जंजीर॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0022","text":"जो उगे सो अस्ते, फूले सो कुम्हलाय।\nजो चुने सो ढहे, जन्मे सो मर जाय॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0023","text":"निंदक नियरे राखिए, आंगन कुटी छवाय।\nबिन पानी साबुन बिना, निर्मल करे सुभाय॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0024","text":"जहां दया तहां धर्म है, जहां लोभ तहां पाप।\nजहां क्रोध तहां काल है, जहां क्षमा तहां आप॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0025","text":"संत कबीर दास ने कहा, तू जीवित छोड़ मोह।\nप्रेम जो सच्चा होवे, मिटे जगत की दोह॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0026","text":"जो तन से नाता तोड़े, जो मन से नाता जोड़े।\nवो ही है सच्चा संत, जग के बंधन जो छोड़े॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0027","text":"कबीर कहे जो जानत है, वो जानत है कुछ नाहिं।\nजो जानत है नाहिं, वो जानत है माहिं॥","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"कबीर दोहे (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0028","text":"चाह मिटी, चिंता मिटी मनवा बेपरवाह ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0029","text":"माटी कहे कुम्हार से, तु क्या रौंदे मोय ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0030","text":"माला फेरत जुग भया, फिरा न मन का फेर ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0031","text":"तिनका कबहुँ ना निंदये, जो पाँव तले होय ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0032","text":"गुरु गोविंद दोनों खड़े, किसके लागों पाँय।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0033","text":"सुख मे सुमिरन ना किया, दु:ख में करते याद ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0034","text":"साईं इतना दीजिये, जा मे कुटुम समाय ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0035","text":"धीरे-धीरे रे मना, धीरे सब कुछ होय ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0036","text":"कबीरा ते नर अँध है, गुरु को कहते और ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0037","text":"माया मरी न मन मरा, मर-मर गए शरीर ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0038","text":"रात गंवाई सोय के, दिवस गंवाया खाय ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0039","text":"दुःख में सुमिरन सब करे सुख में करै न कोय।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0040","text":"सुख मे सुमिरन ना किया, दु:ख में किया याद ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0041","text":"लूट सके तो लूट ले, राम नाम की लूट ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0042","text":"जाति न पूछो साधु की, पूछि लीजिए ज्ञान ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0043","text":"बडा हुआ तो क्या हुआ जैसे पेड़ खजूर।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0044","text":"पाँच पहर धन्धे गया, तीन पहर गया सोय ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0045","text":"कबीरा सोया क्या करे, उठि न भजे भगवान ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0046","text":"कबीरा खड़ा बाजार में, सबकी मांगे खैर।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0047","text":"धीरे-धीरे रे मना, धीरे सब कुछ होय।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0048","text":"जो उग्या सो अंतबै, फूले सो कुमलाय।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0049","text":"जग में बैरी कोई नहीं, जो मन शीतल होय ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0050","text":"जहाँ काम तहाँ नाम नहिं, जहाँ नाम नहिं वहाँ काम ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0051","text":"कामी, क्रोधी, लालची, इनसे भक्ति न होय ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0052","text":"साधु ऐसा चाहिए जैसा सूप सुभाय।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0053","text":"जो तोको काँटा बुवै ताहि बोव तू फूल।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0054","text":"उठा बगुला प्रेम का तिनका चढ़ा अकास।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0055","text":"सात समंदर मसि करूँ लेखनि सब बनराइ।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0056","text":"साधू गाँठ न बाँधई उदर समाता लेय।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0057","text":"सुख में सुमिरन ना किया, दु:ख में करते याद।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0058","text":"तिनका कबहुँ ना निंदये, पाँव तले जो होय।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0059","text":"बड़ा हुआ तो क्या हुआ जैसे पेड़ खजूर।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0060","text":"जिन खोजा तिन पाइया, गहरे पानी पैठि।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0061","text":"पोथी पढ़ि पढ़ि जग मुआ, पंडित भया न कोय।","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — दोहे","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0062","text":"कबीर की आध्यात्मिक क्षुधा और आकांक्षा विश्वग्रासी है। वह कुछ भी नहीं छोड़ना चाहती, इसलिये वह ग्रहणशील है; वर्जनशील नहीं, इसलिये उन्होंने हिन्दु, मुसलमान, सूफी, वैष्णव, योगी प्रभृति सब साधनाओं को जोर से पकड़ रखा है। -- आचार्य क्षितिमोहन सेन","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0063","text":"हिन्दी साहित्य के हजारों साल के इतिहास में कबीर जैसा व्यक्तिव लेकर कोई उत्पन्न नहीं हुआ। -- आचार्य हजारी प्रसाद द्विवेदी, 'कबीर' में","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0064","text":"कबीरदास बहुत-कुछ को अस्वीकार करने का अपार साहस लेकर अवतीर्ण हुए थे। उन्होंने तत्काल प्रचलित नाना साधन-मार्गों पर उग्र आक्रमण किया है। -- आचार्य हजारी प्रसाद द्विवेदी","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0065","text":"तिस पर कबीरदास जी स्वयं पढ़े-लिखे न थे। उन्होंने जो कुछ कहा है वह अपनी प्रतिभा और भावुकता के वशीभूत होकर कहा है। उनमें कवित्व उतना नहीं जितना भक्ति और भावुकता थी। उनकी वणी हृदय में चुभने वाली है। -- बाबू श्यामसुन्दर दास","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0066","text":"मनुष्यत्व की भावना को आगे करके निम्न श्रेणी की जनता में उन्होंने आत्मगौरव का भाव जगाया। -- आचार्य रामचन्द्र शुक्ल","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0067","text":"हिन्दी भक्ति काव्य का प्रथम क्रान्तिकारी पुरस्कर्ता कबीर हैं। -- डाॅ. बच्चन सिंह","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0068","text":"कबीर की वचनावली की सबसे प्राचीन प्रति सन् 1512 ई. की लिखी है। -- आचार्य रामचन्द्र शुक्ल","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0069","text":"इसमें कोई सन्देह नहीं कि कबीर ने ठीक मौके पर जनता के उस बड़े भाग को सँभाला जो नाथपंथियों के प्रभाव से प्रेमभाव और भक्ति रस से शून्य शुष्क पड़ता जा रहा था। -- रामचन्द्र शुक्ल","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0070","text":"उन्होंने भारतीय ब्रह्मवाद के साथ सूफियों के भावात्मक रहस्यवाद, हठयोगियों के साधनात्मक रहस्यवाद और वैष्णवों के अहिंसावाद तथा प्रपत्तिवाद का मेल करके अपना पंथ खड़ा किया। -- रामचन्द्र शुक्ल","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0071","text":"भाषा बहुत परिष्कृत और परिमार्जित न होने पर भी कबीर की उक्तियों में कहीं-कहीं विलक्षण प्रभाव और चमत्कार है। प्रतिभा उनमें बड़ी प्रखर थी इसमें सन्देह नहीं है। -- रामचन्द्र शुक्ल","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0072","text":"कबीर की रचनाओं में भारतीय निर्गुण ब्रह्मवाद, सूफियों का रहस्यवाद, योगियों की साधना, अहिंसा आदि की बातें होते हुए भी स्वामी की दृष्टि से सगुण ब्रह्म का उल्लेख हो गया है। -- लक्ष्मी सागर वार्ष्णेय","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0073","text":"जहाँ कबीर की राख को समाधिस्थ किया गया था वह स्थान बनारस में अब तक कबीर चौरा के नाम से प्रसिद्ध है। -- डाॅ. श्यामसुन्दर दास","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0074","text":"हिन्दी साहित्य के हजार वर्षों के इतिहास में कबीर जैसा व्यक्तित्व लेकर कोई लेखक उत्पन्न नहीं हुआ। महिमा में यह व्यक्तित्व केवल एक ही प्रतिद्वन्द्वी जानता है तुलसीदास। -- हजारी प्रसाद द्विवेदी","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0075","text":"कबीर ने ऐसी बहुत बाते कही है जिनसे समाज सुधार में सहायता मिलती है पर, इसलिए उनको समाज सुधारक समझना गलती है। -- हजारी प्रसाद द्विवेदी","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0076","text":"कबीर की भाषा संत भाषा है। भाषा की यह स्वाभाविकता आगे चलकर प्रेमचन्द में ही मिलती है। -- डाॅ. बच्चन सिंह","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0077","text":"कबीर की भाषा का निर्णय करना टेढी खीर है, क्योंकि वह खिचड़ी है। -- डाॅ. श्यामसुन्दर दास","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0078","text":"कबीर प्रधानतः उपदेशक और समाज सुधारक थे। -- लक्ष्मी सागर वार्ष्णेय","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0079","text":"भारतीय धर्मसाधना के इतिहास में कबीरदास महान विचारक एवं प्रतिभाशाली महाकवि हैं। -- डाॅ. नगेन्द्र","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0080","text":"वे सिर से पैर तक मस्तमौला, स्वभाव से फक्कड़ फकीर थे। -- हजारी प्रसाद द्विवेदी","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0081","text":"भाषा पर कबीर का जबरदस्त अधिकार था। वे वाणी के डिक्टेटर थे। -- हजारी प्रसाद द्विवेदी","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0082","text":"साम्प्रदायिक शिक्षा और सिद्धान्त के उपदेश मुख्यतः ’साखी’ के भीतर है, जो दोहों में है। इसकी भाषा सधुक्कड़ी अर्थात् राजस्थानी पंजाबी मिली खड़ी बोली है। -- आचार्य शुक्ल","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0083","text":"निर्गुण पंथ में जो थोड़ा-बहुत ज्ञान पक्ष है वह वेदान्त से लिया हुआ है। जो प्रेत तत्त्व है, वह सूफीयों का है। अहिंसा, और प्रप्रति के अतिरिक्त वैष्णवता का और कोई अंश उसमें नहीं है। उसके सुरति और निरति शब्द बौद्ध सिद्धों के हैं। -- आचार्य शुक्ल","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0084","text":"कबीर का रहस्यवाद प्रायः शुष्क और नीरस है। -- डाॅ. चन्द्रबली पाण्डेय","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0085","text":"यह कहना कि वे समाज-सुधारक थे गलत है। यह कहना कि वे धर्म-सुधारक थे, और भी गलत है। यदि सुधारक थे तो रैडिकल सुधारक। वे धर्म के माध्यम से समाज में क्रांतिकारी परिवर्तन लाना चाहते थे। -- डाॅ. बच्चन सिंह","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0086","text":"वे (कबीर) भगवान के नृसिंहावतार के मानो प्रतिमूर्ति थे। -- आचार्य हजारी प्रसाद द्विवेदी","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0087","text":"जो लोग कबीरदास को हिंदू- मुस्लिम धर्मों का सर्व-धर्म समन्वयकारी सुधारक मानते हैं वे क्या कहते हैं; ठीक समझ में नहीं आता। कबीर का रास्ता बहुत साफ था। वे दोनों को शिरसा स्वीकार कर समन्वय करनेवाले नहीं थे। समस्त बाह्याचारों के जंजालों और संस्कारों को विध्वंस करनेवाले क्रांतिकारी थे। समझौता उनका रास्ता नहीं था। इतने बड़े जंजाल को नाहीं कर सकने की क्षमता मामूली आदमी में नहीं हो सकती। -- आचार्य हजारी प्रसाद द्विवेदी","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0088","text":"ऐसे थे कबीर। सिर से पैर तक मस्तमौला, स्वभाव में फक्कड़, आदत से अक्खड़, भक्त के सामने निरीह, भेषधारी के आगे प्रचंड, दिल के साफ, दिमाग के दुरुस्त, भीतर से कोमल, बाहर से कठोर, जन्म से अस्पृश्य, कर्म से वंदनीय। -- आचार्य हजारी प्रसाद द्विवेदी","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0089","text":"कबीर की सैद्धांतिक या दार्शनिक मान्यताएँ अद्वैतवाद के अनुकूल हैं। व्यावहारिक क्षेत्र में कबीर पूर्णतः प्रगतिशील दिखाई पड़ते हैं। -- डाॅ. गणपतिचन्द्र गुप्त","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0090","text":"हजरीप्रसाद द्विवेदी का नाम कबीर के साथ उसी तरह जुड़ा है जैसे तुलसीदास के साथ आचार्य रामचन्द्र शुक्ल का नाम। -- नामवर सिंह","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0091","text":"चूँकि कबीर का तिरस्कार मुख्यत: उनकी अटपटी भाषा और कवित्वहीनता को ही लेकर किया गया था, इसलिए 'कबीर' नामक ग्रंथ में द्विवेदीजी ने इस पक्ष की सविस्तार और सोदाहरण चर्चा की। अब तक कबीर की 'डाँट-फटकार' और 'खंडन-मंडन' की चर्चा तो बहुत हुई थी, किन्तु उनके व्यंग्यों का कहीं जिक्र भी नहीं आया था। द्विवेदीजी ने पहली बार कबीर के व्यंग्यकार रूप को प्रस्तुत करते हुए घोषित किया : \"सच पूछा जाय तो आज तक हिंदी में ऐसा जबर्दस्त व्यंग्य लेखक पैदा ही नहीं हुआ। उनकी साफ चोट करनेवाली भाषा, बिना कहे भी सब कुछ कह देनेवाली शैली और अत्यन्त सादी किंतु अत्यन्त तेज प्रकाशन भंगी अनन्य-साधारण है। हमने देखा है कि बाह्याचार पर आक्रमण करनेवाले संतों और योगियों की कमी नहीं है, पर इस कदर सहज और सरल ढंग से चकनाचूर कर देनेवाली भाषा कबीर के पहले बहुत कम दिखाई दी है। व्यंग्य वह है, जहाँ कहनेवाला अधरोष्ठों में हँस रहा हो और सुननेवाला तिलमिला उठा हो और फिर भी कहनेवाले को जवाब देना अपने को और भी उपहासास्पद बना लेना हो जाता हो। --  नामवर सिंह","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"kabir-hi-0092","text":"वस्तुत: कबीर ने मधुमक्खी के समान अपने समय में विद्यमान समस्त धर्म साधनाओं और निजी के योग से अपनी भक्ति का ऐसा छत्ता तैयार किया है जिसका मधु अमृतोपम है, जिसका पान कर भारतीय जन मानस कृत कृत्य हो उठा है। यह मधु अक्षुण्ण है, युगों से भारतीय इसकी मधुरिमा का रसास्वादन कर रहे हैं। -- कबीर साहित्य के मर्मज्ञ गोविन्द त्रिगुणायत","author":"Kabir Dohas — Hindi","source":"Hindi Wikiquote — Kabir — कबीर दास के बारे में उक्तियाँ","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:wisdom","theme:devotion"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."}]}